{"tid":1423561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京以「光復香港」上綱上線圖抹黑 梁天琦選舉經理人親解口號由來","createTime":"2019-08-06T14:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:24:25.000Z","uid":212249,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4a9a7201196491d94f71e40f8229f0fddf60a37e","tid":1423561,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190806/large/1565085038_88d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190806%2Flarge%2F1565085038_88d2.jpg&h=eeeb2810&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港澳辦今日於記者會上一大重點是針對示威者提出的「光復香港，時代革命」口號，認為是衝着「一國兩制」的「一國」而來，目的一目了然、路人皆知，反問「想光復什麽，光復到哪去？」圖扯至港獨問題，民主派召集人毛孟靜指，遺憾北京仍然拒絕理解香港情況，只一味將示威者的訴求、口號「無限上綱上線」，將香港示威視為衝着「一國」而來：「咁樣係對抗爭者不公平。」她強調「光復香港」的口號，意思是要「反暴、反黑」，「時代革命」則是還香港高度自治，並非要搞港獨。<br />\n<br />\n工黨張超雄也批評，特區政府試圖把今次運動扭曲為香港人與國家的矛盾，轉移視線，令人無視林鄭的錯誤，「整場運動都係林鄭處理『送中』條例反彈連番犯錯，呢個係同國家主權無關。佢就要將市民憤怒轉化為針對國家主權，佢就可以繼續放黑社會出嚟、強硬打壓，告人暴動罪。」<br />\n<br />\n曾任梁天琦選舉經理人的何蔓兒於facebook發帖，解構近日成為中央矛頭的「光復香港，時代革命」口號來源，明顯與港獨無關。何憶述2016年1月初梁天琦宣佈參選新東補選時，有關口號尚未出現，當時公佈的選舉口號為「知行合一，世代革新。」至1月下旬，梁相約時任青年新政召集人梁頌恆等商討選舉策略，認為原口號不夠搶耳、立場不夠鮮明，故共同構思新選舉口號。何指，由於梁天琦參加補選主要目的是宣場本土理念及其組織，而本民前當時最為人熟悉的是曾在2015年於屯門、沙田、元朗、上水等地區發起光復行動，所以欲於選舉口號用上「光復」字眼以作提醒；而由於是新東補選，曾構想用上「光復新東」字眼，「但因為嗌起黎﹙嚟﹚唔夠順口，最後就再放大到用『光復香港』」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190806/59903968?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2nJxMOfQZhQVHJs4HC8fn_9kcb0ztXyL98sHBFurF9vslFDnoUwG87mWo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190806%2F59903968%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2nJxMOfQZhQVHJs4HC8fn_9kcb0ztXyL98sHBFurF9vslFDnoUwG87mWo&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=467552d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190806%2F59903968%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2nJxMOfQZhQVHJs4HC8fn_9kcb0ztXyL98sHBFurF9vslFDnoUwG87mWo&h=9c82dccc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190806/59903968?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2nJxMOfQZhQVHJs4HC8fn_9kcb0ztXyL98sHBFurF9vslFDnoUwG87mWo</a>"},{"pid":"64f5103e3d09704ce58fb3712fcbae3f1d3cc693","tid":1423561,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:21:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"30bf1780a66870befed689b39ef23f32fae79473","tid":1423561,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:24:35.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"37dd2cbc121f515c8703f389573dca07448bc637","tid":1423561,"uid":299469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:25:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a143c42ac8c8ef84cebf9069b2c205810807bcc","tid":1423561,"uid":147803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"719d3f8b44315f7f3ea7dd0e07bfd8b1790767fe","tid":1423561,"uid":83998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:26:29.000Z","msg":"光復香港 世代革新<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd72044b66d257945a24810a58afed53abb60aa3","tid":1423561,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"719d3f8b44315f7f3ea7dd0e07bfd8b1790767fe","tid":1423561,"uid":83998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:26:29.000Z","msg":"光復香港 世代革新<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583c9aa902e95f677b03334122ad5109d190bafa","tid":1423561,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d1ff7690ea8d05f93df436d6b599acfc4c0a0e12","tid":1423561,"uid":205275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:41:05.000Z","msg":"佢地越講 就代表我哋行緊既方向越係正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3be1b13aaaba367a9b23f7fa2840726192840ef2","tid":1423561,"uid":30006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:42:29.000Z","msg":"解乜鳩丫，要屈你講乜都死"},{"pid":"c0c74c4001b3703e649d2affbd285ffbf1166a9f","tid":1423561,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"老老實實 難民之父真係講得好啱喎"},{"pid":"186bf6bc30e321139be9362415f00865e3fa7301","tid":1423561,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:24:25.000Z","msg":"其中一個方向係<br />\n正名「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n光復香港 = 回復以往繁榮既香港<br />\n方法: 首4大訴求<br />\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例的修訂，以至法理上終止條例程序<br />\n二、收回612暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷對之前及今後所有反送中抗爭者控罪 <br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警察濫權<br />\n<br />\n時代革命=香港體制要改革<br />\n方法: 第五大訴求<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行真正的雙普選<br />\n<br />\n而唔係林鄭所誤解既港獨<br />\n<br />\n建議之一, 請其他巴打更改<br />\n<br />\n重溫 616, 71, 721 宣言, 文宣請加油, 令我們的行動合理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1423473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1423473</a>"}]}